        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The system calls this method during adaptation so the delegate can configure properties of the adaptive presentation controller before it presents."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "For example, the system automatically adapts a view controller that presents as a popover in standard size classes to a sheet in compact size classes. You can implement this method to customize the sheetâ€™s properties before it presents."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
